{"tid":1632274,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔講廢話, 我剩係要保證過到人權法!","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:53:49.000Z","uid":11454,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7a709abe65860f5f0ee2d628bdb5c49a350cd0e0","tid":1632274,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人要嬴, 就一定要過人權法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5841f7c87b7d1ed342f3122ce43058d7908598ce","tid":1632274,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ea2d9d833d7c92ba456f6bd70250a435b0d8451","tid":1632274,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef393057e04d17094fa6650c7db6c7ee55b627a","tid":1632274,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9a299eb9363e35582dd1036ebdc04fae3271d3c","tid":1632274,"uid":142010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:47.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"bcf745f7f8aa641a66b5ec4d4455dab1b28377ea","tid":1632274,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"29f53ac84555ed801f7db324eef499ed3bf5faa4","tid":1632274,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒(人權法)呀<br />\n麻煩各位裝修佬暫時停工呀<br />\n18區唱歌呀"},{"pid":"1ada7f8fc5c4fb98ca03b28426d4a4077fd78466","tid":1632274,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f53ac84555ed801f7db324eef499ed3bf5faa4","tid":1632274,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒(人權法)呀<br />\n麻煩各位裝修佬暫時停工呀<br />\n18區唱歌呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"蒙面法前後戴口罩嘅意義唔同咗 而依個意義應該決定我地嘅行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea2d96158b04a8045bc12ece1b37159e74e1b2c3","tid":1632274,"uid":294765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"我地要將個重點放返政權同黑警惡行！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631985</a>"},{"pid":"8984eb00d06358c194ff43d9817265663c92abf9","tid":1632274,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9b4d3f8b3d15c4f7c3398943b9f4cff54f4690a","tid":1632274,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:44.000Z","msg":"[公投] 黎緊幾日勇武定和理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5998421c63d8974120e2aef71f9d4b92204f0faf","tid":1632274,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有人權法過左，香港政商先有機會重新歸邊！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e47eccb13f0b9023505ea8488d4de7b8ef6f6955","tid":1632274,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要過到人權法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675b4c735ed9b3d4c7e7b20a89a3905929e112cb","tid":1632274,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"179d2a418d2a10038bd4775999df5ebd5857f8c7","tid":1632274,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要過到人權法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8769d4800d0cc3395c5d4b52e0959b73ce666334","tid":1632274,"uid":137859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b60df3bd5671386933305ad96b22609a6f87308","tid":1632274,"uid":285027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dc668558bb526ed0fc41c33f4846a8200fdd28","tid":1632274,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒巴, 外國文宣組, Gphone, hocc, sharon EE, 仲有好多好多手足幫手<br />\n咁多個月做左咁多野<br />\n一定要過到人權法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8622fe692290ad8d8a1e7748bbc28c2414ccd2","tid":1632274,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"724483fe221ef45628ad6d06336d3083a29148a0","tid":1632274,